        As to the noble Lord's amendment, I can put on record that the Government will not use this Bill to impose a statutory levy or charge on private business to fund the financial assistance scheme. Neither does Clause 274 enable us to introduce a levy by secondary legislation even should we wish to&#x2014;and I have made it clear that we will not.
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0665P0-03073'>
